articles.author: Frank Pallotta, CNN
articles.title: 'Us' scares up screams and applause at SXSW premiere - CNN
articles.description: Jordan Peele is up to his old tricks. The director of "Get Out" was in Austin, Texas on Friday to premiere his latest horror and psychological thriller, "Us."
articles.content: It should surprise no one that US is a very satisfying (and anxiety-inducing) follow up to GET OUT. What's more fascinating: that a high-concept FUNNY GAMES/Hitchcock/Cronenberg/Bradbury mashup could feel so fresh at the same time. #sxsw — erickohn (@erickohn… [+14 chars]
